title: OnlyFans Future | Sal Vulcano & Chris Distefano Present: Hey Babe! | EP 74
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!
The BABES are here to spice up your Saturday!!! Chrissy Chaos tells us about his big Puerto Rican adventures from his vacation with his family. Sal and Chris learn about OnlyFans and how it will be a big part of all our futures. Bhad Bhabie makes over 50 million dollars on OnlyFans. Chris tells us about the power of abstinence and how it can make everything in your life better......Al Roker pooped his pants at the White House. Elton John is a GOD. Chris is excited for his upcoming trip to Savannah. Chris talks about the worst bomb of his career. Should the babes start an OnlyFans?!?!? The babes watch the worst of OnlyFans and things get CREEPY! WOW!!! Merch is out now babes!!! Check the store on Sal's website. SalVulcanoComedy.com
